myPhotoShop

The goal of this project is to reproduce a simple version of photoshop.

I have implemented the following features :

2 - Better open/close
4 - Better saving
6 - Better History
7 - Status Bar
8 - Draw
9 - Erase
11 - Polygons

I also have implemented the following bonuses:

- The transparency for all colors.
- The fill Bucket.
- The french flag filter.
- Export an image as png/jpg.
- Shorcuts for menus.
- All features have a icon associated.